Clause 3(d)(1) of rule XIII of the Rules of the House of Rep-
resentatives requires an estimate and a comparison of the costs
that would be incurred in carrying out H.R. 2392. The Committee
has requested but not received a cost estimate from the Director
of the Congressional Budget Office. However, pursuant to clause
3(d)(1) of House rule XIII, the Committee will adopt as its own the
cost estimate by the Director of the Congressional Budget Office
once it has been prepared.
